    "Discontinued classic analog drives are replaced by AxCent drives.",
    "Replacement depends on mode of operation. Default (Current / Voltage / Duty Cycle) maps to the AxCent 'AB*' drive. IR Compensation / Tachometer Velocity on brushed-only analog drives maps to a brushed-only 'A*' AxCent drive.",
